OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F500 more UK wildfires this 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fyear than all of 2021      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, There have been almost 500 more        
OL,6, wildfires this year than the whole of  
OL,7, 2021, a fire chief has said.           
OL,9,FMark Hardingham, chair of the National 
OL,10,FFire Chiefs Council (NFCC), said hot   
OL,11,Fand dry weather had combined to create 
OL,12,Fthe perfect conditions for wildfires.  
OL,14,FSo far in 2022, he said there had been 
OL,15,F745 wildfires in the UK - more than a  
OL,16,F200% increase from the total figure of 
OL,17,F247 for all of last year.              
OL,19,FFire chiefs are urging people not to   
OL,20,Fbring combustible items to open spaces.
